io.github.mountainrange.mule.gameplay

Class PlainTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.mountainrange.mule.gameplay.PlainTile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tile

    public class PlainTile
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tile
    An alternate Tile implementation, which does not use JavaFX. This tile does not actually draw anything to the screen; it is only a sample implementation of Tile. This is useful for Junit Tests.
